title: Protest against Catalonian independence in Madrid
description:
(30 Sep 2017) Protesters gathered in Madrid on Saturday to demonstrate against Catalonian independence - a day before a referendum is due to take place.
The referendum has been endorsed by the Catalan separatists and they vow to go ahead with the ballot but the Spanish government considers the referendum illegal and the country's Constitutional Court has suspended it.
